                        <span class="home-tool-card__cta-hint">Sans inscription · PDF</span>
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="home-tool-card__cta-arrow" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </a>
                </article>

                <article class="tool-card motion-card home-tool-card" data-home-reveal>
                    {% include 'home/partials/_tool_icon.html.twig' with { tool: 'qqoqccp' } %}
                    <h3 class="home-tool-card__title">Analyse QQOQCCP</h3>
                    <p class="home-tool-card__desc">Cadrez un diagnostic avec les 7 questions essentielles pour formaliser une première analyse.</p>
                    <div class="tool-card__tags">
                        <span class="home-tool-tag">Sans inscription</span>
                        <span class="home-tool-tag">Rapport généré</span>
