                    </a>
                </article>

                <article class="tool-card motion-card home-tool-card" data-home-reveal>
                    {% include 'home/partials/_tool_icon.html.twig' with { tool: 'pareto' } %}
                    <h3 class="home-tool-card__title">Diagramme de Pareto</h3>
                    <p class="home-tool-card__desc">Visualisez les causes qui concentrent l'essentiel de vos problèmes pour prioriser vos actions.</p>
                    <div class="tool-card__tags">
                        <span class="home-tool-tag">Sans inscription</span>
                        <span class="home-tool-tag">Analyse 80/20</span>
                        <span class="home-tool-tag">Export PDF</span>
